The smoke-test I decide to include are following:
- Check the correctness of copying its standard input to its standard output
- Check the correctness of carrying out --input
- Check the correctness of carrying out --output
- Check the correctness of carrying out --input --output
- Check the correctness of dealing with invalid arguments
- Check the correctness of carrying out fault handling for --catch --segfault
- Check the correctness of dealing with non-existing input
- Check the correctness of dealing with unwritable output

